  "title": "Sales Consultant [Recruitment] - Basic $2500 - $3000 + Commission, East, 5days",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p><ul><li>Basic $2500 - $3000 + Commission, East, 5days</li><li>5 working days, 9am-6pm</li><li>Entry level is welcome to apply, training will be provided</li><li>Location : Taiseng (Walking distance from Taiseng MRT)<br /></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Achieve monthly sales targets while contributing to the company’s overall revenue goals.</li><li>Manage the end-to-end recruitment process, from candidate sourcing through to successful placement.</li><li>Conduct executive and non-executive search assignments across a wide range of industries.</li><li>Handle the job offer process, including salary negotiations and compensation discussions with both clients and candidates.</li><li>Advise clients and candidates on market trends, salary benchmarks, and current employment conditions.</li><li>Drive business development by acquiring new clients and growing relationships with existing accounts.</li><li>Build and maintain strong client partnerships through effective account management.</li><li>Work closely with clients to design customized recruitment strategies and hiring plans.</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No experience required, training will be provided</li><li>Candidates with CEI Certificate and recruitment experience will have added advantage</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Comfortable to work in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p><br /><strong>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button</strong></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>StaffKing Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Cheang Wei Yang (R21102313)</strong></p>",
